Imi ibabaten-nneɣ i ɣ-d-isɛan țțaken-aɣ tiyita yerna nqudeṛ-iten, amek ur nețqadaṛ ara Ṛebbi yellan d lǧens n mkul ṣṣenf.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
Eɛni sɛan azal n xemsa alaf n yergazen i gețwassenden di ddunit ? Neɣ akteṛ n ɛecṛa alaf yemdanen i gumnen s Sidna Ɛisa ?
Aṭas ara yedṛun deg-sen wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Tawṛat-agi ẓẓayen, qṛib a d-iffeɣ leɛqel, daymi i ț-id-sissenǧasen awal.
Ger widak-nni i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Antyuc, bɣan ad beccṛen lexbaṛ n lxiṛ ; aṭas ara d-yasen, ad beccṛen lexbaṛ n lxiṛ n Lmasiḥ, ad beccṛen i wat Isṛail di tmurt-nni, ad qqimen anagar akteṛ n wiyaḍ.
Atah wayen ara sen-d-iniɣ : llan gar-awen yergazen n tegzirt n Kritus akk-d waɛṛaben, ma d wiyaḍ a ten-issemneɛ seg-sen. ?ef wayagi i gečča akk-d lḥecma, dɣa ččan-ten seg uksum n tissit.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Ad illuẓen yellan d lkețțan aṛqaq n temtunt ( iɣes ) ara ččen cwiṭ n lqut, daymi a d-heggin ayen yelhan ma ț-țisirt i genneɛtaben iman-nsen. S wakka aț-țennalem alamma ț-țaggara, aț-țeččem aț-țeččuṛen s ddheb.
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla asteqsi, mbla ma tḥebbṛem, aț-țețeččem seg-s.
Di mkul amkan nesla yedṛa leḥṛam d ameqqran gar-asen, d ayen ur nețțaf ara ulamma ger wat Isṛail neɣ d yiwen deg-wen ? Mačči armi geɣli lḥal mazal ițțalas i yiman-is.
Awi lḥeqq-ik tṛuḥeḍ. I ma yella bɣiɣ ad fkeɣ i uneggaru annect i k-fkiɣ i kečč ?ader aț-țḥekmeḍ fell-i, a k-rreɣ d lɛaddat n Sidi Ṛebbi !
?ef wayagi, ilaq-aɣ a nelmed amek ara nsel s ufus n wemdan, iwakken a nefcel imi, mačči s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi i d-yekka lameɛna a nețkel ɣef Ṛebbi.
Awi lḥeqq-ik tṛuḥeḍ. I ma yella bɣiɣ ad fkeɣ i uneggaru annect i k-fkiɣ i keččini ; sseǧhed-iyi deg umkan-ik, sbeɛdet iman-ik ɣef rrif n lebḥeṛ.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam, awi-yi-d yid-sen aqenduṛ, abeɛda wid yețwaxedmen s weglim akk-d lbabuṛ, ur d-yeǧǧi ara ad sseɣliɣ.
Ini-yasen daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ur ilaq ara ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ur ilaq ara ad țḥawalent tissit n ccṛab meɛna ilaq ad nehhunt ɣer wayen yelhan,
Lxuluq-nni, mkul m'ara slen i wawal a t-imger iman-is ; m'ara d-imɣumen sebba n tuccḍa ula d wiyaḍ ; m'ara xedmen deg-s akken i lmend n wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Imdanen țgallan s wayen i ten-yugaren, s limin i ferrun tilufa ;
?ef ddemma n weqṛaḥ n tɛebbuṭ-ik i k-issefcalen, ur tess ara kan aman lameɛna sew ciṭṭuḥ n ccṛab.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt daɣen ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ. Axiṛ-iten ad yefk i lǧețța-s, lmut m'ara rren lxiṛ-nsen d asfel i yiman-nsen, lmut.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt daɣen ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ. A Anɣṛum i gzemren ad kksen allen-is, ad mmten akken ilaq.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
D nețța i ɣef d-nnant tira iqedsen : D azṛu-nni i tḍeggṛeḍ allen-ik ɣef tmurt-ik, m'ara yawi tamusni-nwen seg wass wis sin, ma d win ara iheggin iman-is isseḥlun iman-ik deg umkan-is.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : « ț-țagi i d tețxebbiṛem s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi, eɛni d lebɣi-k i tella di ddunit ? »
Yerna m'ur sɛint ara ayen ara xedment, ad țcalint seg weɣṛum ara ččen.
Amdan yezmer ad iḥeṛṛeb yal ṣṣenf n lewḥuc : ama d wid iteddun ɣef ṛebɛa iḍaṛṛen, ama d ifṛax, ama d izerman ama d lewḥuc n lebḥeṛ yerna ț-țideț iɣleb-iten meṛṛa.
A nuggad ad ṭṭfen imukan ger sin, ad kksen ayla n wid ifelleq akk-d ddheb, si lɛinseṛ n lqut neɣ tissit n teṛwiḥt-agi, țɛețțib iman-nsent iwakken a d-yeqqim kan leɛyubat-nsen.
Yefhem belli leɛtab, d sɛaya tameqqrant yugaren igerrujen n tmurt n Maṣeṛ. Meɛna acḥal tewseɛ meǧhud-ik iwakken aț-țemfaṛaqem ɣer mkul tama.
Yella wayen i d-ibeggnen annect agi, axaṭer yeffeɣ-ed tikufta n tlatin yuklal di teswiɛt-nni, seg wezgen ur yezmir ara a d-isbeggen iman-is ma d yiwen seg wass.
Ssizdeget iman-nwen, kkset si gar-awen tamtunt ( iɣes ) taqdimt n ddnub iwakken aț-țilim d arukti di liman nwen.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ. Lameɛna ass-a daɣen ilaq ad yili d sebba n tikli-nneɣ akk-d leḥrir.
Agdud a d-yili aṭas n yemdanen, aṭas deg wayen i d-iteddun ɣer webrid n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Tesɛa-d takmamt tameqqrant n leswaṛ n temdint n Ludikus, Illafɛa-nni ț-țilawin yumnen s Lmasiḥ, leɛfeṛ n temdint n Ludikus, iɛebbak-nni taẓallit ț-țamezduɣt n tɛebbuṭ n temdint n Ludikus.
M'ara d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, bɣan ad awḍen ɣer leqsed nsen. Refden amextaf n temdint n Birɣamus abeḥnuq (d tamsalt-is ) axaṭer yebɣa ad iqdec ɣef wannect-agi, win akken i t-ițeddun ɣer temdint n Birɣamus. Deg unejmaɛ-nni, a ten-yawi ɣer wanda yebɣa ad yawi lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, win ara iɛiwnen di lexṣaṣeṛb n temdint n Birur.
Eɛni ayen akk i tenɛețțabeḍ iṛuḥ baṭel ? Ur ḥsiɣ ara iṛuḥ baṭel !
ulac daɣen win ara yaɣen lqeṛfa, leɛqaqeṛ, leɛṭeṛ, lmuṛ, lebxuṛ, ccṛab, zzit, awren eṛqiqen akk-d yirden, izgaren, ulli akk-d tutlayt. M'ara yili gar-awen isegman, ur țțafen ara ayen ara yedṛun wayen yuran di ddunit.
?ef wannect-agi i gella d amcafeɛ gar-awen, ur ilaq ara ad ḥadrent iman-ik ɣef wannect-agi iwakken a d-yedṛu yid-ek leḥzen neɣ m'ulac ț-țikellax.
M'ara d-taseḍ, amenzu yella ccetwa di tnac yid-sen, ilaq daɣen ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es mbla lɛib, aț-țessiweḍ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, tețțekkim di lbir-nsen.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Ma yella kečč i d-ițwagezmen seg uḥeccad, tețțuleqmeḍ ɣef tɣawsiwin timecṭuḥin, sya d asawen aț-țheggiḍ iman-ik am yiman-ik.
Ssufɣen-d yiwet n tbuciḍant iɛeddan ccetwa di tegzirt-nni ; ma ț-țigzirt-nni iṛuḥ a d-yaweḍ ɣer wesqif.
Neɣ daɣen di ddunit-agi m'ara țwaqehṛeɣ neɣ ț-țimes, neɣ m'ulac wid yellan seddaw n tudert neɣ tiṛwiḥin-agi, alamma ț-țaggara n leslak i ɣ-d-yelmeɣ.
Ass n lḥisab, qṛib a d-yaweḍ wayen i ț-iɛemmṛen ɣef lluḥ, iwakken ad țwaqehheṛ. Ma yella yiwen n wawal yekka-d s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi, aț-țesɛeddim kra n wid ifennun.
Imdanen llan tețțen, țessen, țemyezwaǧen, zeggjen i dderya-nsen, armi d akessar ; ḥebbṛen iman-nsen s wakken yella leḥsab i s-d-ifkan.
D lbaṭel zerɛen ara d-megren, țțafen lfeṛḥ-nsen mi xeddmen ɛinani lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen. Sčuṛen d lɛib akk-d lḥecma, yerna m' ara qqimen yid-sen ɣer lmakla, ur țsetḥin ara s lehduṛ-nsen d ukellex-nsen.
Iɛedda-d syenna yiwen umsebrid i d-yuɣalen si lexla, isem-is d lbabuṛ neɣ d azeggaɣ,
M'ara bdunt fessunt, qṛib a d-yaweḍ unebdu ɣer tmezduɣt-nni, ad yaweḍ win akken i wen-d-yehwa.
M'ara yeččaṛ, iḥewwaten a t-id-jebden ɣer imensi n Tfaska.
Xemmemet ihi ɣuṛ-es aț-țwalim amek i geqbel leɛtab n yemdanen imednuben, axaṭer ger leǧnas ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail sekkeṛ ayen akk i k-d-nnan ɣer tewwurt.
Ma yella wamek ara t-yawi ț-țirebbaɛ i d-ikecmen ɣer tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen neɣ d aɛessas n tmura i d-iteddun.
arrac imeẓyanen, deg umkan-agi meṛṛa ur nelli ara seg wemṛaḥ agi, ilaq ad iɛeddi di ccṛeɛ iwakken a d-immeslay ɣef wayagi meṛṛa.
Deg ussan-nni, yiwen ur yeqqaṛ i wayeḍ neɣ i wid ara yeznuzun fell-as s lxiṛ ur țțafen ara deg-s wayen ara s-d ssukksen, iwakken ma yella wayen ara yedṛu yid-es. Ilaq ad yili d sebba n usteqsi,
Walit tigerfiwin , iskker-ed tijeḥnaḍin-agi s tjeḥnaḍen, akk-d tnezmar n igenwan anda yella wemkan i deg xeddmen leɛcuc-is.
Akken daɣen i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n igenni.
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-awen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nsen. Cban asigna yețțawi waḍu, ur d-yețțak lehwa ;
Mi gɛedda lweqt, yuɣal-ed umɛellem-nni, isnejmaɛ-iten-id iwakken ad imḥasab yid-es.
Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, meẓẓi neɣ meqqeṛ, d igellil neɣ d ameṛkanti, d akli neɣ d aḥeṛṛi, ad wwten ticṛaḍ deg ufus ayeffus neɣ deg unyir-is.
A lḥakem ameqqran ! S uḍebbaṛ-ik yelhan i d-yers lxiṛ d lehna ɣef tmurt-agi ! Ɣef wayagi, a Filiks ameqqran, ncekkeṛ-ik meṛṛa di mkul amkan ;
Wiyaḍ anagar ɣef teflukin nniḍen, iṛuḥ si tmurt n Misskokowi, wwḍent-ed ɣer lmeṛṣa n Kritus ; am akken i t-issinfeṛṛuṛen d lexṣaṣ, qqiment-ed daɣen iferrawen-ed ifennunt,
Ur sṭuqqutet ara awal mbla lmeɛna ɣef wayen yeɛnan izuṛan n lejdud neɣ čaqlalat.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, ur țsetḥin ara s uḥellel-nsen iwakken a d-tban tmanegt n wid yesɛan cci akk-d lewḥuc.
Yerna m'ara d-nekcef ayen xeddmen, lecɣal-nsen țbanen-d di lecɣal n wiyaḍ iwakken ad qqimen deg-nsen anagar wid i gxeddmen lecɣal-agi s tezmert-nsen. Tanemmirt-ed daɣen lemtel-agi i d-iteddun s uselmed-agi ur stehzayet ara di tira iqedsen : ayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Taktabt-agi tektabin, nețbeggin-ed belli nefka-ed belli d nukni ițbeggin-ed belli nefka-ed belli nefka-ed kan belli nefka-aɣ anagar s wul ur ccbiɛ ara.
Meɛna ur qebbel ara i tejmaɛt aț-țɛawen tuǧǧal meẓẓiyen di leɛmeṛ, meɛna m'ara bɣunt ad ɛawdent zzwaǧ zemrent ad ǧǧent abrid n leslak.
Ma yella tebɣiḍ ssebɛed fell-ak, tzemreḍ aț-țesfehmeḍ ddheb, neɣ m'ulac akal yeččuṛen d idɣaɣen, alamma tețwaxelṣeḍ-it iwakken a k-id-yaweḍ.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen.
Akken qqaṛen : « Ciṭṭuḥ n temtunt ( iɣes n temtunt ) yessalay akk arukti.»
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i tmes, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n ddunit meṛṛa.
A d-yas lweqt i deg ara sen yețwakkes yesli, deg wayen ara sen-d-ssukksen.
Llant gar-aneɣ acḥal d abrid i t-iɛedda si lebḥeṛ ɣer tmurt n Birɣamus, si tmurt n iṛeqqen yellan di tmurt n wezṛu yellan ț-țamurt n tmes, dinna ara yilin gar-aneɣ ciṭṭuḥ n Sidna Ɛisa.
?emcabin ɣer lebḥeṛ s wayes i gulin ɣer temdint n Tiberyas iwakken ad zwiren azal n snat n temda n Tlatin litrat n leɛṭeṛ i d-yerbeḥ. Zdafen tigzirt n Kritus, s ɛeggden-ț-id tis tlata n tlatin.
Akken qṛib ad yaweḍ gma-s ɣer tnezduɣt-nni, qṛib a d-yeɣli wurrif n Sidi Ṛebbi ; lameɛna ur ɛawdeɣ ara deg waggur d acu ara xedmen m'ara ṛuḥen ɣer mkul amkan.
Yal yiwen leswaṛ-is ṛeqqmen s yezṛa ɣlayen n mkul ṣṣenf. Amezwaru s Lyaman n Jasb, wis tlata s lyaman n Agat, wis ṛebɛa n ?umṛud,
Ur țɣawal ara aț-țesserseḍ wiyaḍ, ur xeddmet ara lxilaf ger lɣaci-agi, ur țțaṭṭafet ara tajɛelt, lameɛna ɣef wid yețɛeddayen syenna.
Neɣ m'ulac wid yellan dagi, a k-issin lexbaṛ ɣef wayen yeɛnan idrimen, axaṭer mačči d ayen i teẓriḍ belli ț-țideț ilaq aț-țeččeḍ.
D lbaṭel zerɛen ara d-megren, țțafen lfeṛḥ-nsen mi xeddmen ɛinani lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen. Sčuṛen d lɛib akk-d lḥecma, yerna m' ara qqimen yid-wen ɣer lmakla, ur țsetḥin ara s lehduṛ-nsen d ukellex-nsen.
Meɛna leǧnas nniḍen ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail ad ḥekmen fell-asen s ddnubat nsen, armi d lmut tis snat, m'ara țțuḥasben lɛiqab n ccariɛa ɣef ddemma n wiyaḍ, ɣef ddemma n ddnubat nsen i gḍuṛṛen aṭas n iseggasen.
Yețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan tazmert a ɣ-yesseǧhed di liman, iwakken a kkun-isseǧhed di leḥmala-ines, ur t-yeǧǧi ara ad yerwi tijmaɛin n tmes.
Imi Brisila d Akilas xeddmen iqiḍunen am Bulus, yeqqim ɣuṛ-sen xeddmen s tdukli.
Lameɛna di tlemmast n ddunit nniḍen ḍeggṛet-ed yiwet n teɣli ajdid. ?ef ddemma-k i tella tezmert n lexṣaṣ, aț-țfeǧǧeǧ i yiwet n tikkelt kan.
Akken yella wemdan n ddunit, ara yilin yemdanen n ddunit ; ɣas akken lǧețța-nsen d iṭijeṛben, yețnerni di teswiɛt n lweqt i deg ara d-yeɣlin fell-asen.
Daymi i glaq ad ssiwḍen ɣer wannect-agi, mmi-s n Biri akk-d țelt n wuzzal deg iḍaṛṛen, meɛna m'ara bɣin-iten d imdukkal-nsen, qebblen iman-nsen d imdukkal-nsen.
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣ tiẓgi tameqqrant, meɛna ɣuṛ-es aṭas n yemdanen i gețɛeddayen syenna.
Daymi m'ara n-awḍeɣ ɣer wayen i ɣ-yuɣalen ɣer webrid imezwura, ɣer zdat ur kcimen ara ɣer daxel n ddunit ; seɛbeɣ melmi ara d-yedṛu wannect-agi, mačči s ɣuṛ-es i d-yekka meɛna d annect-agi i gella.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n ddunit, aṭas ara iɛiwnen deg-sen. Llan daɣen wid i gzemren ad ɛiwnen di tigellilt.
M'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni, a wen-yaf teṭṭfem di teṛwiḥt-ik akk-d tiseḍwa, abeɛda wid yețwaxedmen s wedɣaɣ, d wedɣaɣal.
Ur țțaket ara ayen yeṣfan i yeqjan, ur ṭeggiṛet ara tiɛeqcin ɣlayen ɣef wayen yeɛnan izuṛan n ddunit.
M'ara k-yessiweḍ wexṣim-ik ɣer ccṛeɛ, eɛṛeḍ a ț-tefruḍ yid-es uqbel aț-țawḍem ɣer dinna, neɣ m'ulac a k-yawi ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen uqiḍun n temlilit i deg llan sin imukan.
Ma yella kečč i d-ițwagezmen ɣuṛ-ek kra n lweqt kan, lemmer ț-țideț tzemrem a d-tefkeḍ idrimen iwakken a t-tefkeḍ idrimen.
Ma yella ayen ur nețdum ara yesɛa ccan, ilaq a kkun-id-yaweḍ ɣer teṭṭfem.
yenna-yas : A wi-yufan a Sidi Ṛebbi, ssizdeg iman-ik di lecɣal-ik neɣ m'ulac ț-țikellax, zeddiget aț-țeččeḍ di ddunit ass-a !
Ma yella kečč i d-ițwagezmen seg uḥeccad, tețțuleqmeḍ ɣef tzemmurt n lɛali ɣas akken d aḥeccad i telliḍ, acḥal ihi i sen-ishel i nutni yellan ț-țiṣeḍwa n tzemmurt iwakken ad uɣalen ad țțuleqmen ɣef tzemmurt-nsen.
