Tqeṛṛbem daɣen ɣer tejmaɛt n wid yextaṛ Ṛebbi d imezwura yesɛan ismawen-nsen uran deg wawal n Ṛebbi. Tqeṛṛbem ɣer Ṛebbi nețța i gzedɣen lexbaṛ n lxiṛ ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail ɣer wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ iwakken a d-mmeslayen timeslayin ur nețwassen ara, seg wayen yuran di tira iqedsen.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi si tmura n Galasya, di tmurt n Ssya, di mkul amkan jemɛen-d wid yumnen s Lmasiḥ, s tikli-inek ur tkeččlen ara ayen n diri armi ṛwan-k ;
S tideț, di yal amkan n ddunit i deg ara sen-ițwakkes tilelli, iwakken a d-ntekkes ara lexṛif seg wakal.
Di lweqt-nni, yiwen wergaz n wat Isṛail yețțusemman Abulus, ilulen di temdint n Maṣeṛ, yusa-d ɣer tmurt n Maṣeṛ, armi d lweqt i deg ilaq ad ițțuɛbed Sidi Ṛebbi a t-neḥmed. ?ef wayagi, ilaq daɣen a d-yedṛu lemtel i wayen i d-tenna ccariɛa.
Akken daɣen i t-yezmer a t-nefhem s tigzirt, ifka-yas ula d yiwen a wen-d-isbeggen s tikli-ines belli ț-țagi i d lewkil s ufus n wemdan, axaṭer d lewḥuc ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail iwakken a t-id-isbeggen s wayagi ;
Sɛut iles aẓidan, timeslayin ur nețwassen ara, sin wudmawen, iwakken tibṛatin-nsent aț-țesbedd lewqam, ayen akk s wayes i tbeddeṛ agdud n Sidi Ṛebbi.
seg yiwet n tilawin i gețmeslay daɣen s tutlayt i s-d-yezzin iwakken ad immeslayen, timeslayin ur nețwassen ara, sin neɣ tlata a d-mmeslayen meɛna yal yiwen s nnuba-s, yerna ad yili d sebba-nsen i wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Akken yuli wass, lḥukkam n Ṛuman ceggɛen wid ara yinin i uɛessas n lbabuṛ ; ini-yasen : Serreḥ-asen i imeḥbas nniḍen ;
Eɛni yezmer yiwen n lɛinseṛ a d-yefk aman ḥlawen akk-d wid ṛẓagen ? Neɣ m'ara rren aman ḥlawen akk-d waman.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt daɣen ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg iḍ, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-nwen iwakken a d-tṛuḥ.
Ma yella tesɛeddaḍ-ik sin wussan, aț-țețțuselkem s ufella n usigna. Ma tebɣiḍ ɣuṛ-wen, tessawḍem tawwurt n uẓekka, m'ara d-yaweḍ ɣer tewwurt, aț-țessiweḍ kra n wussan yid-wen iwakken ad ṛuḥeɣ a d-yekcem.
Llan deg-s lewḥuc at ṛebɛa idaṛṛen n mkul ṣṣifa, wid iteddun ɣef wuɛebbuḍ, akk-d yefṛax n igenni s mkul ṣṣifa.
Ɣas akken ṛṛusul nnan asen azal n ṛebɛa alaf n yemdanen, meɛna ula d yiwen deg-sen xuṣṣen aṭas,
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Tețɣuṛṛu imezdaɣ n tmura-agi s twaɣit aț-țfeǧǧeǧem yerna aț-țeldiḍ ṭwabeɛ-ines, axaṭer lweqt i deg ara d-yewḍen s tmes yecban times n uɛeqqa n uxerḍel.
A d-nefk lemtel n dduzan n lmusiqa am tjewwaqt d snitra : ma yella ur yemxalaf ara ttejṛa, ur nețțuɣal ara a d-yedṛu yid-es.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n Sudum d Gumuṛ, i ten-id-yezzin, anagar ticmatin d zzna, qqiment-ed d lemtel mi tent-yessenger Sidi Ṛebbi s tmes yecban times n ǧahennama ;
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n lmut.
Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lxell. Dmen-d ameččim n taḍuṭ cudden-t ɣer yixef n uɣanim, sbezgen t-id s lxell-nni, ssawḍen-as-t ɣer tmes.
A d-tilint zzelzlat timeqqranin, a d-ɣlin di yal lehlakat i gderrɛen ( i gneṭṭḍen) akk-d laẓ, a d-tilint leɛǧubat yessexlaɛen akk-d laẓ ;
Akken i d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, ɣilen ad awḍen ɣer leqsed nsen.
Aṭas seg wid yellan xeddmen ssḥur, wwin-d tiktabin-nsen s wayes xeddmen ssḥur, sseṛɣen-tent zdat medden. Ufan belli azal n ṛebɛin yid-sen ččuṛen d ṭṭmeɛ.
Leɛqiṛa tis snat, tețțunefk-as tezmert a s-tefk ṛṛuḥ i yemdanen, si tama nniḍen n lmut, s wakka ur tețțili ț-țaɛkumt ula i yiwen.
seg yiwet n tama reggmen-kkun, kksen fell-awen sser, si tama nniḍen tbeddem ɣer tmurt n Kanada iwakken a d-tbanent tissas, zdat inesbeɛ.
Ilaq ula d kečč ad țwajeṛben di leqdic-nsen, m'ur ufin ara ayen ara sen-d-ssukksen imiren zemren ad qedcen di tejmaɛt.
